83
00:06:45,620 --> 00:06:46,980
Since we have come to this point,

84
00:06:50,340 --> 00:06:50,940
I believe it.

85
00:06:53,140 --> 00:06:54,620
As long as we keep going,

86
00:06:56,580 --> 00:06:58,980
