87
00:07:02,660 --> 00:07:03,940
Come on. Cheers.

88
00:07:05,100 --> 00:07:05,459
Cheers.

89
00:07:05,820 --> 00:07:06,860
I finally saw

90
00:07:06,900 --> 00:07:07,540
