91
00:07:08,820 --> 00:07:09,820
We've been fighting monsters and upgrading to the next level.

92
00:07:10,420 --> 00:07:10,820
Come on.

93
00:07:11,100 --> 00:07:11,540
Cheers.

94
00:07:11,620 --> 00:07:12,420
The good men will be rewarded.

95
00:07:12,820 --> 00:07:13,260
Come on.

96
