113
00:07:54,740 --> 00:07:55,820
Fatty Wang, just you wait!

114
00:07:55,820 --> 00:07:57,300
Have some water and have some fun.

115
00:08:01,780 --> 00:08:02,500
Naive!

116
00:08:15,220 --> 00:08:16,020
Sang.

117
00:08:16,820 --> 00:08:17,940
Well done!

118
00:08:18,180 --> 00:08:20,260
