121
00:08:27,580 --> 00:08:28,100
Liu Sang.

122
00:08:28,540 --> 00:08:29,620
Look under the water.

123
00:08:29,780 --> 00:08:30,780
Is there a tunnel?

124
00:08:32,340 --> 00:08:33,180
Be careful.

125
00:08:54,660 --> 00:08:55,300
Are you alright?

126
00:08:55,940 --> 00:08:56,540
What did you see?

127
00:08:59,540 --> 00:09:00,220
I saw that

128
00:09:00,900 --> 00:09:01,700
there are many bodies

129
00:09:02,940 --> 00:09:04,300
under the water.

130
00:09:06,060 --> 00:09:07,140
There is a cave over there

131
00:09:07,660 --> 00:09:08,940
which looks deep.

132
00:09:09,140 --> 00:09:10,820
I guess it leads to another space.

133
00:09:12,780 --> 00:09:14,020
I'll take a look with you.

134
00:09:47,420 --> 00:09:47,940
Over here.

135
00:10:45,860 --> 00:10:46,980
What the hell is this place?

136
00:10:47,140 --> 00:10:48,220
Why are there so many bodies?

137
00:10:48,700 --> 00:10:50,740
They are various in degree of corruption.

138
00:10:51,500 --> 00:10:53,380
They didn't die at the same time.

139
00:10:55,340 --> 00:10:56,060
My guess is

140
00:10:56,220 --> 00:10:58,260
this is the entrance to the core area of Thunder City.

141
00:10:59,220 --> 00:11:00,420
These bodies

142
00:11:00,420 --> 00:11:02,540
came here making a pilgrimage to Thunder City at different times.

143
00:11:03,420 --> 00:11:05,140
They came here

144
00:11:05,140 --> 00:11:05,580
with their regrets and desires.

145
00:11:06,660 --> 00:11:09,060
But they didn't expect they would die here.

146
00:11:11,060 --> 00:11:14,020
So that's how Thunder City reverses all regrets.

147
00:11:16,020 --> 00:11:16,700
Since you die,

148
00:11:16,860 --> 00:11:19,020
of course all your regrets die with you.

149
00:11:19,180 --> 00:11:19,740
Am I right?

150
00:11:22,260 --> 00:11:22,780
Bro.

151
00:11:23,860 --> 00:11:24,980
Where is the entrance?

152
00:11:25,300 --> 00:11:26,620
They wouldn't have died

153
00:11:26,820 --> 00:11:28,020
if the entrance is obvious.

154
00:11:28,460 --> 00:11:30,300
Everyone, be cautious.

155
00:11:47,620 --> 00:11:48,340
Fatty.

156
00:11:48,500 --> 00:11:49,900
Aren't we looking for the entrance?

157
00:11:50,140 --> 00:11:52,140
Why do you keep rummaging through the bodies?

158
00:11:52,820 --> 00:11:54,460
I want to see if they carried any valuable items with them.

159
00:11:56,700 --> 00:11:59,260
Don't you think it's quite a high risk to reverse one's regrets?

160
00:12:00,540 --> 00:12:01,540
I need to

161
00:12:01,580 --> 00:12:02,980
see if I can find any antiques.

162
00:12:03,100 --> 00:12:04,180
I'll put them in my pocket if I find any.

163
00:12:05,060 --> 00:12:05,980
Maybe

164
00:12:06,140 --> 00:12:07,780
we will decide to go back the next second.

165
00:12:08,300 --> 00:12:09,500
Then I'll get nothing from this adventure.

166
00:12:09,500 --> 00:12:11,020
That'll be really a regret.

167
00:12:11,100 --> 00:12:13,300
As the saying goes, a thief will never return empty-handed.

168
00:12:14,420 --> 00:12:15,540
I guess these dead people's regret

169
00:12:15,700 --> 00:12:17,660
was that they were all poor when alive.

170
00:12:22,460 --> 00:12:23,700
I did find a treasure.

171
00:12:23,860 --> 00:12:24,460
What is it?

172
00:12:24,620 --> 00:12:25,340
Come on!

173
00:12:25,380 --> 00:12:25,820
Come here!

174
00:12:38,500 --> 00:12:39,340
Bai.

175
00:12:48,980 --> 00:12:49,940
Wu Sanxing?

176
00:12:58,380 --> 00:12:59,300
Mr. Jiao.

177
00:12:59,980 --> 00:13:01,900
We are running out of food.

178
00:13:02,420 --> 00:13:04,460
If we can't find the way to Thunder City,

179
00:13:05,100 --> 00:13:07,580
we will run out of supplies soon.

180
00:13:32,820 --> 00:13:35,380
We'll follow the direction of thunder to find it.

181
00:13:37,580 --> 00:13:39,460
Wherever the thunder goes,

182
00:13:40,980 --> 00:13:43,020
it's where we are going.

183
00:13:45,100 --> 00:13:45,780
Understood.

184
00:14:25,140 --> 00:14:27,100
I spent a few days in the Dumb Village.

185
00:14:27,580 --> 00:14:29,540
It's full moon again tonight.

186
00:14:31,860 --> 00:14:34,340
I don't know why, but it reminds me of the moon I saw in Wuzhou.

187
00:14:37,460 --> 00:14:39,140
Maybe I got homesick.

188
00:14:44,540 --> 00:14:47,220
I didn't expect one day I would

189
00:14:47,900 --> 00:14:50,580
miss home alone in a place far away from home.

190
00:14:54,860 --> 00:14:56,460
The wind is chilling.

191
00:14:57,260 --> 00:14:58,420
I'm going back to sleep.

192
00:15:05,180 --> 00:15:07,100
I dreamt of the whole family last night.

193
00:15:09,220 --> 00:15:11,340
Mom scolded me again in front of everyone.

194
00:15:13,740 --> 00:15:15,300
But I wasn't very upset this time.

195
00:15:15,900 --> 00:15:17,660
I could sense that although she was scolding me,

196
00:15:17,820 --> 00:15:19,460
actually she was just worried about me.

197
00:15:19,940 --> 00:15:21,700
So I didn't say anything.

198
00:15:24,700 --> 00:15:26,900
When I woke up in the morning, it rained again in the Dumb Village.

199
00:15:28,580 --> 00:15:31,180
I even thought of what Mom told me in my dream and

200
00:15:31,700 --> 00:15:33,420
took an umbrella when I went out.

201
00:15:39,140 --> 00:15:41,700
I even obeyed Mom's request in the dream.

202
00:15:43,300 --> 00:15:44,940
Maybe I'm really getting old.

203
00:15:57,060 --> 00:15:58,460
I can't remember

204
00:15:58,460 --> 00:15:59,980
how many years have passed since I was forced to look for Thunder City.

205
00:16:02,260 --> 00:16:03,620
Yang Daguang died of illness.

206
00:16:06,580 --> 00:16:08,060
Mu Xuehai went crazy.

207
00:16:10,140 --> 00:16:12,020
I am the only one left.

208
00:16:17,420 --> 00:16:19,180
I spent the prime of my youth

209
00:16:19,580 --> 00:16:22,340
in such an absurd thing.

210
00:16:24,420 --> 00:16:26,020
This fake weather observation team

211
00:16:26,180 --> 00:16:27,900
has run out of patience, too.

212
00:16:33,740 --> 00:16:35,660
In the afternoon I finally persuaded some villagers

213
00:16:35,660 --> 00:16:37,100
to take me down the underground river.

214
00:16:40,500 --> 00:16:42,460
We rested by the river bank.

215
00:16:42,820 --> 00:16:45,140
I was woken up by the moonlight reflection underwater.

216
00:16:47,060 --> 00:16:50,140
I saw hordes of jellyfish which were very beautiful.

217
00:16:54,460 --> 00:16:55,980
I remembered Wenjin used to say that

218
00:16:56,260 --> 00:16:58,020
she loved watching jellyfish swim.

219
00:16:59,460 --> 00:17:02,340
She thought they were very intelligent creatures.

220
00:17:04,060 --> 00:17:05,180
I didn't expect that today

221
00:17:05,180 --> 00:17:06,860
I saw a fair share of jellyfish alone.

222
00:17:11,180 --> 00:17:12,460
When I go back from Thunder City,

223
00:17:12,660 --> 00:17:14,580
I want to take this experience to show off to her.

224
00:17:22,020 --> 00:17:24,460
Today is Xie's birthday.

225
00:17:25,860 --> 00:17:27,780
Before I left, I promised to celebrate his birthday with him.

226
00:17:28,610 --> 00:17:30,340
I definitely can't make it this time.

227
00:17:33,020 --> 00:17:35,460
Maybe I'll never go back.

228
00:17:41,340 --> 00:17:44,340
That kid must be scolding me in his heart now.

229
00:17:45,460 --> 00:17:47,820
But his Uncle Sanxing has lied to him so many times.

230
00:17:48,020 --> 00:17:49,700
He should be used to it.

231
00:17:50,140 --> 00:17:51,620
He will accept it.

232
00:18:01,740 --> 00:18:04,900
