Piaopiao, don't go.

241
00:19:29,580 --> 00:19:31,220
Piaopiao.

242
00:19:59,660 --> 00:20:00,540
Xie.

243
00:20:01,460 --> 00:20:02,780
Go to Thunder City.

244
00:20:04,500 --> 00:20:05,460
Stay alive.

245
00:22:01,060 --> 00:22:01,700
Go away!

246
00:22:03,460 --> 00:22:03,900
Come on.

247
00:22:04,020 --> 00:22:04,860
Go away!

248
00:22:05,100 --> 00:22:05,540
Come to me.

249
00:22:05,660 --> 00:22:06,300
Go away!

250
00:22:06,780 --> 00:22:07,540
Go away!

251
00:22:26,460 --> 00:22:27,300
Liu Sang.

252
00:22:31,300 --> 00:22:32,180
Liu Sang.

253
