261
00:23:28,540 --> 00:23:29,380
Liu Sang!

262
00:23:34,300 --> 00:23:35,100
Mr. Third Junior!

263
00:23:37,900 --> 00:23:39,500
Wu Xie, help me!

264
00:23:41,820 --> 00:23:42,740
Help me.

265
00:23:43,060 --> 00:23:43,700
Liu Sang!

266
00:23:43,740 --> 00:23:44,460
Give me your hand!

267
00:23:45,580 --> 00:23:46,820
Set your feet on the rock.

268
00:24:02,460 --> 00:24:03,340
